# Security Policy

## Supported Versions
This is a student project and is maintained on a best-effort basis.

## Reporting a Vulnerability
If you discover a security issue:
1. Do not publicly post it immediately.
2. Contact the developer via: tgbosi.2400042@stu.cu.edu.ng

## Notes
- Avoid storing sensitive information in tasks.
- If Local Storage is used, tasks are visible to anyone using the same browser profile.